					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The last time I saw discussion of this, I saw people used DPCM samples to generate ramps to adjust the current position. This let them choose quiet tones that were enharmonic with the current chord during the ramp instead of sudden pops.<br /><br />The volume of such a ramp should be very roughly equal to 0.5 on the pulse channels' volume scale.</div>

